<strong>Hunter skill</strong>

Place tier-appropriate traps; prey approaches; trap snaps. Catches grant Hunter XP on the OSRS curve (level cap 99). Type <strong>/hunter</strong> in chat to see your level and XP.

<strong>Bird snares</strong> (single-tile, fast cycle)
Copper 45%, Tin-Bronze 55%, Iron 65%, Steel 72%, Mithril 80%, Adamantite 87%, Runite 94%.

<strong>Box traps</strong> (5×5 attractor area, baited)
Iron 50%, Steel 62%, Mithril 74% (chinchompas at L53), Adamantite 85%, Runite 93%. No snap-on-fail; resets automatically.

<strong>Ava's Attractor</strong> (Hunter device, worn on torso)
Pulls dropped projectiles back to the wearer's inventory; slowly attracts low-value metal junk on the move. Disabled by torso armor.
